      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm type 1 and i had a tiny dinner tonight, like just a handful of crackers. i usually take my basal insulin at night but i'm worried about going too low since i barely ate anything. is it okay if i just skip my basal dose tonight so i dont crash while i sleep?",
